/**
 * CMS content list — a DataTables grid whose DATA loads over AJAX from the /api
 * service (Cms_Service_Page::datatable), per the client/server paradigm: the server
 * renders only this shell; the browser fetches rows as a Tiger Webservice.
 *
 * Filtering + sorting are all server-side: the global search box spans every public
 * text column, the Status/Type toolbar scopes the working set (wired via the
 * tigerDataTable `extraData` hook), and every data column is sortable. Action
 * controls are built client-side from per-row permission flags the service computes
 * (can_edit / can_delete) — authorization stays server-side.
 */
?>
